title: Father Vegetarian Kitchen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Chinese, Take-out, Tibetan
description: Cozy place with limited seating. Owner is a young Tibetan who set up this small eatery with the intention to make clean, good, and affordable vegetarian food for all Tibetans. Menu is only written in Tibetan and Chinese, and the staff do not speak English. Address in Chinese is 北京中路措美林9号.
streetAddress: Beijing Middle Road, Cemenlin 3rd Alley, 9, Lhasa
